<br>
It's a high level zone (50+), but if you have been a good monk and maxxed your FD you can zone in, FD and ask nicely if you may loot a club if it drops for anyone that cant/wont loot it. The clubs are NODROP and LORE so some still rot on the ground.<br>
<br>
The club is 12 damage 23 delay with a +5 AC and +2 STR. I think weight is 2,5 or something.<br>
<br>
I have done this for both my monks, Jondalar in his mid 40s and Izzit in his early 20s. At lower levels this is a real killer, and Jon will probably use his until he gets the epic.<br>
<br>
We could also get a group together and hunt the Gorangas til you get a club. One group of 50+ would do nicely I think. I wouldn't mind going if we can find a suitable time.<br>
